1.59
log
@fix the spacing of -m in the SYNOPSIS
@
text
@.\"	$OpenBSD: rcs.1,v 1.58 2013/01/18 11:21:09 guenther Exp $
.\"
.\" Copyright (c) 2005 Jean-Francois Brousseau <jfb@@openbsd.org>
.\" Copyright (c) 2005 Xavier Santolaria <xsa@@openbsd.org>
.\" All rights reserved.
.\"
